<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nouveau commentaire sur votre post</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header .subtitle {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .post-info {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 5px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .post-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #1976d2;
            font-size: 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .post-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1565c0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .post-content {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #bbdefb;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            max-height: 150px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        .comment-section {
            background-color: #f1f8e9;
            border-left: 5px solid #4caf50;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .comment-section h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #2e7d32;
            font-size: 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .comment-meta {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #c8e6c9;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .meta-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .meta-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .meta-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2e7d32;
            min-width: 80px;
        }
        .comment-content {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px solid #a5d6a7;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1b5e20;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .action-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🔔 Nouveau commentaire sur votre post</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">Votre publication a reçu une nouvelle réponse</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="post-info">
                <h3><span class="icon">📋</span> Informations sur le post</h3>
                <div class="post-title">{{ post_title }}</div>
                <div class="post-content">{{ post_content }}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="comment-section">
                <h3><span class="icon">💬</span> Nouveau commentaire</h3>
                
                <div class="comment-meta">
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">Auteur:</span>
                        <span class="highlight">{{ comment_author_name }}</span>
                        {% if comment_author_email %}
                            <span style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">({{ comment_author_email }})</span>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">Date:</span>
                        <span>{{ comment_date|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="comment-content">{{ comment_content|nl2br }}</div>
                
                <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <a href="#" class="action-button">Voir le commentaire sur le forum</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: #fff3e0; border-left: 5px solid #ff9800; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #e65100; font-size: 14px;">
                    <strong>💡 Astuce:</strong> Vous pouvez répondre directement à ce commentaire depuis le forum.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement par le système de notification du forum.</strong></p>
            <p>Post ID: {{ forum_id }} | Commentaire ID: {{ comment_id }}</p>
            <p>Pour ne plus recevoir ces notifications, veuillez contacter l'administrateur du site.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11px; color: #999;">
                Cet email a été envoyé à {{ post_author_name }} 
                {% if comment_author_email and comment_author_email != forum.email %}et en copie à {{ comment_author_name }}{% endif %}.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
